    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AbstractQuestionParser
    Template class for parsing question files into Category objects.
    AnswerQuestionCommand
    Evaluates a Player's answer for the current Turn's Question, and updates the Player's score
    Category
    Category to which Questions may belong.
    CLIController
    Handles UI interaction through the console
    Command
    Abstract class for the Command design pattern implementation.
    CommandCreationException
    Thrown when a Command fails to be created by CommandCreator
    CommandCreator
    Instantiates and returns concrete Commands with supplied paramaters.
    CommandExecutionException
    Thrown when a Command fails
    CommandInvoker
    Invoker for the Command design pattern implementation.
    CSVEventLogWriter
    Creates and writes to the process mining log to a CSV file
    CSVParser
    Parser for CSV-based Jeopardy question files.
    DOCXReportGenerator
    Generates game reports in .docx format using Apache POI.
    EnterPlayerNameCommand
    This Command creates a new Player given a player name.
    EventLogBuilder
    Prepares command data for CSV writing
    EventLogEntry
    Data for each column of the process mining log
    ExitGameCommand
    Sets the GameState to indicate the game is over, by calling GameState.setIsOver(boolean)
    FileParserCreator
    Instantiates the correct AbstractQuestionParser given a file path.
    Game
    Controls game flow by instantiating the necessary Commands and using a CommandInvoker to execute them
    GameQuitException
    Thrown when a player quits the game early
    GameState
    Holds all the info required for the running of a Game.
    GenerateEventLogCommand
    Generates the process mining log CSV, given a list of Commands and a gameID
    GenerateReportCommand
    Generates the game report
    InvalidFileFormatException
    Thrown when a an Invalid File Format is specified for some purpose
    JSONParser
    Parser for JSON-based Jeopardy question files.
    LoadFileCommand
    Loads question data into GameState
    Main
     
    PDFReportGenerator
    Generates game reports in .pdf format using PDFBox.
    Player
    Holds relevant player information
    Question
    Holds question data
    ReportGenerator
    Strategy interface for generating game reports in different formats.
    ReportGeneratorCreator
    Instantiates the correct ReportGenerator given a format.
    SelectCategoryCommand
    Verifies a given Category exists in the current GameState, then updates the current Turn by calling Turn.setTurnCategory(group20.GameLogic.Category)
    SelectPlayerCountCommand
    Sets the player count for the GameState, verifying it is between 1-4.
    SelectQuestionCommand
    Verifies a given Question exists in the current GameState, then updates the current Turn by calling Turn.setTurnQuestion(group20.GameLogic.Question)
    StartGameCommand
    Indicates the start of the game, calling GameState.setIsOver(boolean) with false
    Turn
    Holds turn data
    TXTReportGenerator
    Generates game reports in .txt format.
    XMLParser
    Parser for XML-based Jeopardy question files.
